59.2	Mario_Batali	Mario Batali	Mario Batali (born September 19, 1960) is an American chef, writer, restaurateur and media personality. In addition to his classical culinary training, he is an expert on the history and culture of Italian cuisine, including regional and local variations. Batali co-owns restaurants in New York City, Las Vegas, Los Angeles, and Singapore. Batali's signature clothing style includes shorts and orange Crocs.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/eb/Mario_Batali%2C_2005.jpg/220px-Mario_Batali%2C_2005.jpg
